properties.name: Current Pad
properties.description: Posted by Pinkshoelaces2186 Northwest Glisan Street Portland OregonI live here currently. Cast of Characters: Jeremy- The fiance. Studies Television Production and Communications. Enjoys 80\'s music (specifically Duran Duran) and the band Bush. Loves movies (favorite is Harold and Maude). Kombucha- The pug dog. Enjoys pooping all over the place and chewing on stuff I just bought and/or my underpants. Named after the Chinese Tea brewed for thirty years that promotes balance and vitality. Seamus- Cat #1. Flame-point siamese. Enjoys sleeping and snubbing people. And eating. Ripley- Cat #2. Has six claws. Enjoys attempting suicide off of our fire escape, picking fights with the other animals, and burrowing under the covers. Jamie- (Me). Enjoys reading, movies, art, and music. Studies Environmental Studies. Likes doing laundry. Likes discovering new places, taking photos, and the color red.

properties.name: Voodoo Doughnuts
properties.description: Posted by Pinkshoelaces   22 SW 3rd Ave, portland, orBest doughnut place ever. Open late (until like 4am). First lost my Voodoo Doughnut virginity: Drunk on my 22nd birthday, a bunch of friends and I went there. They have doughnuts like the following: The Cock and Balls (a doughnut shaped like, well, a cock and balls; naturally, it\'s cream-filled), The Mango Tango, a captain crunch covered doughnut, a peanut butter oreo doughnut, etc.
